            <note anchored="true">
               <term xml:lang="jpa">*אבלי</term>? Sophocles 276-277: “aula, the court, the royal or imperial residence or head-quarters”. Not listed in the dictionaries. The reading <term xml:lang="jpa">אהלו</term> is presumably a misreading or a later emendation.
   </note>
